    "synopsis": "Lord Azariel of House Brobantis is dead, and his widow Chettamandey knows exactly who killed him: she did. The frail, brilliant Navigator expects to inherit his power, until ritual murders begin targeting the Navis Nobilite and harvesting their warp-eyes. On Vorlese, the Chaos-touched Radimir Niklau turns the aftermath of his Galimo Prime rite into a campaign of surgical assassinations, forcing Chettamandey into a house-politics investigation where every ally has a price. A court-intrigue mystery inside the Navigator Houses, with old age, ambition and warp-sight made dangerous.",
